WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
I will not be at your father's trial tomorrow.

2
00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.599
When you don't know it, you tried to attack.

3
00:00:05.599 --> 00:00:09.000
Please, don't drop my father's case, please.

4
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:11.000
I want you out of my house by tomorrow.

5
00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:12.990
No.

6
00:00:12.990 --> 00:00:14.990
I want you to leave me.

7
00:00:20.899 --> 00:00:34.679
Please, please come back.

8
00:00:34.679 --> 00:00:35.679
Take it easy.

9
00:00:35.679 --> 00:00:39.979
Your fever just went down.

10
00:00:39.979 --> 00:00:43.140
You've been asleep for three days.

11
00:00:43.140 --> 00:00:45.140
Three days, but my father's child.

12
00:00:45.140 --> 00:00:46.140
It's over.

13
00:00:46.140 --> 00:00:50.310
He was acquitted.

14
00:00:50.310 --> 00:00:52.079
Really?

15
00:00:52.079 --> 00:00:56.270
But I thought that you were the only lawyer who could win the case.

16
00:00:56.270 --> 00:00:57.270
I handled it myself.

17
00:00:57.270 --> 00:01:01.219
Why?

